	<li>Play and charge compatible iPod and iPhone models with Lightning connector including iPhone 5, iPhone 5S, iPhone 5C and iPod touch 5<sup>th</sup>¬†Gen</li>
	<li>2.1 Stereo speaker with 3 inch subwoofer, bass port and bass control</li>
	<li>Dual pairing Bluetooth wireless technology</li>
	<li>Experience the full integrity of original digital audio with the AptX¬Æ Bluetooth codec (when using compatible devices)</li>
	<li>Aux-in for use with other smartphones, tablets and music players</li>
</ul>
